<core:FragmentDefinition xmlns="sap.m" xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" xmlns:u="sap.ui.unified" xmlns:tnt="sap.tnt" height="100%"
	xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<Panel >
		<content>
			<Panel >
				<html:h5>Meter Testing</html:h5>
				<html:div class="apply">
					<html:div class="row">
						<html:div class=" col-md-2 tata1">
							<html:image src="images/tata_logo_white.png" alt="tata_logo" class="img-responsive"></html:image>
						</html:div>
						<html:div class=" col-md-1 pull-right tata2">
							<html:image src="images/tata_emblem_white.png" alt="tata_logo" class="img-responsive"></html:image>
						</html:div>
					</html:div>
				</html:div>
				<html:h6 class="indicate">*Indicates Mandatory Fields</html:h6>
				<html:div class="detailrequire">
					<html:div class="detailspremises">
						<html:h5 class="indicate2">Meter Testing</html:h5>
						<html:hr/>
					</html:div>
					<html:div class="boxpad">
						<html:div class="row ">
							<Label class="col-md-4" text="Consumer No." labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4">
								<Input id="mtconsumernoInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
							</html:div>
						</html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" text="Name" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtnameInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" text="Flat/Shop No." labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtflatshopInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" text="Building Name" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtbuildingnameInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
							<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" text="Street" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtstreetInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" text="City" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtcityInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" text="Postal Code" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtpostalcodeInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" required="true" text="Applicant Name" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtapplicantnameInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" required="true" text="Contact No" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtcontactnoInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4"  text="Email Id" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="mtemailidInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div> 
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4"  text="Meter Serial No" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4">
								<Select class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom" width="100%"  id="meterSrialNoId"
									forceSelection="false"
									selectedKey="{/ProductCollection/0/ProductId}"
									items="{
										path: 'SupplyCatSerachdata>/results',
										sorter: { path: '' }
									}">
									<core:Item key="{SupplyCatSerachdata>DomvalueL}" text="{SupplyCatSerachdata>Ddtext}" />
								</Select>
						</html:div></html:div> 
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4"  text="Meter Type" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="meterTypeInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div> 
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4" required="true" text="Phase Of Supply" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Input id="phaseofsupplyInput" required="true" type="Text" class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom"/>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4"  text="RequestFor" labelFor="input-a"/>
							<html:div class="col-md-4"><Select class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom" width="100%" id="requestFor"
									forceSelection="false"
									selectedKey="{/ProductCollection/0/ProductId}"
									items="{
										path: 'SupplyCatSerachdata>/results',
										sorter: { path: '' }
									}">
									<core:Item key="{SupplyCatSerachdata>DomvalueL}" text="{SupplyCatSerachdata>Ddtext}" />
								</Select>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<Label class="col-md-4"  text="I would like to witness" labelFor="input-a"/>
							
							<html:div class="col-md-4">
								<Select class="sapUiSmallMarginBottom col-md-4" width="100%"  id="witnessforId"
									forceSelection="false"
									selectedKey="{/ProductCollection/0/ProductId}"
									items="{
										path: 'SupplyCatSerachdata>/results',
										sorter: { path: '' }
									}">
									<core:Item key="{SupplyCatSerachdata>DomvalueL}" text="{SupplyCatSerachdata>Ddtext}" />
								</Select>
						</html:div></html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
								<html:div class="col-md-12"><html:h3 >Terms and Conditions.</html:h3>
						</html:div>	</html:div>
					   <html:div class="row">
					   		<html:div class="col-md-12">
					   			<html:p >1.For Meter testing in Laboratory, I am willing to pay the applicable testing charges as per the Regulatory Schedule of Charges.
The charges will be billed to me in the Electricity bill.</html:p>
							<html:p>( i.e. a. Single Phase Meter – Rs.200/-</html:p>
							<html:p>b. Three Phase Meter – Rs.500/-</html:p>
							<html:p>c. Trivector/MD/TOD Meter – Rs.1000/-</html:p>
							<html:p >2. For testing the meter at my site / premises, I am willing to pay the applicable testing charge as per the Regulatory Schedule
of Charges. The charges can be billed to me in the Power Supply bill.</html:p>
							<html:p>( i.e. a. Single Phase Meter – Rs.100/-</html:p>
						<html:p>b. Three Phase Meter - Rs. 350/-</html:p>
					   <html:p>3. In case, the consumer is unable to witness the testing, Tata Power will complete the testing and forward a copy of the test
report within 7 working days of testing to the consumer's billing address.</html:p>
						<html:p  >Note: This online facility of Meter Testing is only for Tata Power meters. In case the meter belongs to R-Infra, the application
form for meter testing needs to be submitted at your nearest Tata Power Customer Relations Center and the testing charges need
to be paid at the R-Infra Office.</html:p>
					   </html:div> </html:div>
						<html:div class="row largebox">
							<html:div class="col-xs-12">	
								<CheckBox id="IdSameAsAbove" text="I/we agree to the above terms and conditions" selected="false"/>
							</html:div>
						</html:div>
						<html:div class="row">
							<html:div class="col-md-3">
								<Button icon="sap-icon://save" text="Submit" press="onSaveNContinue" class="switchcenter"
									ariaDescribedBy="defaultButtonDescription genericButtonDescription"></Button>
							</html:div>
						</html:div>	
					</html:div>
				</html:div>
			</Panel>
		</content>
	</Panel>
</core:FragmentDefinition>